					<div class="principle-item">
						<span class="principle-number">2</span>
						<div>
							<span class="principle-name">Implementation Intentions</span>
							<span class="principle-desc">Declaring what you will work on creates an if-then plan that bypasses willpower</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="principle-item">
						<span class="principle-number">3</span>
						<div>
							<span class="principle-name">Accountability</span>
							<span class="principle-desc">Social commitment to follow through &mdash; stating your intention to others increases success by up to 95%</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="principle-item">
						<span class="principle-number">4</span>
						<div>
							<span class="principle-name">Focused Work Stints</span>
							<span class="principle-desc">Structured deep work blocks calibrated to attention capacity</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="principle-item">
						<span class="principle-number">5</span>
						<div>
							<span class="principle-name">Time Blocking</span>
							<span class="principle-desc">Dedicated scheduled periods that protect deep work from shallow intrusions</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="principle-item">
						<span class="principle-number">6</span>
						<div>
							<span class="principle-name">Power of Play</span>
							<span class="principle-desc">Interactive breaks that activate ancient reward circuits and restore creative capacity</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="stat-callout observe-fade">
					<span class="stat-number">95%</span>
					<p class="stat-description">
						Of FLOWN users reported above-average improvement in focus.
						94% reported improved productivity; 85% rated their quality
						of work as higher.
					</p>
					<cite class="stat-cite">FLOWN user outcomes data</cite>
				</div>

				<!-- Illustration: Two parallel lines with wave connection -->
				<figure class="book-illustration" aria-label="Two figures working side by side">
					<svg class="focus-illustration" viewBox="0 0 200 160" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
